This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of classifiers and regression models, which are common in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) research. The paper also discusses the use of Expectation-Maximization (EM) algorithms, which are commonly used in Neural Networks (cs.NE) and Statistical Learning (cs.SI) research. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, and cs.SI, in that order.
